title: Exception throws when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: When attempting to export data from a table that contains a highlight or map in the attached report, an exception is thrown.
EB: The export should proceed without any exceptions being thrown, and the data should be successfully exported.
SR:
Steps to reproduce: 
1. Open the attached report. 
2. Navigate to the table that contains a highlight or map. 
3. Attempt to export the data from the table. 
4. Observe the exception being thrown.
